{"tid":2422058,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中印爭議邊境撤兵 專家：中國察覺拜登政府強硬態勢","createTime":"2021-02-25T02:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T03:40:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"19b0f5c27c965efda21b3d404664ebe8eeac2649","tid":2422058,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國與印度去年於邊界發生死亡衝突，兩國21日分別宣布，均已完成從喜馬拉雅山邊境爭議地段撤兵，表明地區緊張局勢略有緩解跡象，外媒引述專家說法指出，中國可能判斷美國拜登政府帶來的威脅很大，才一再避免對印事態激化。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n《德國之聲》進一步引述印度海軍退休將領、印度智庫政策研究協會負責人巴斯卡爾（C. Uday Bhaskar）此前接受BBC訪問時的分析論點，他認為，中國在對印政策方面，一直在觀望拜登政府的對中政策是否維持前總統川普時期的強硬路線。<br />\n<br />\n巴斯卡爾解釋，若拜登繼續保持對中國強硬政策，中國認為來自美國的威脅很大，便不可能希望開闢新戰場與印方擴大對抗，以上論述或可與當前中印雙雙撤兵作印證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3448791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3448791&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFdEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=ec174894\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3448791&h=abbf7a8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3448791</a>"},{"pid":"224ba18dc49230c8d0a25c90476815ef11441105","tid":2422058,"uid":2654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"牙登訓係度都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270a8fce167384ee864ef11a36a99b2cc8bcc9e6","tid":2422058,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:41:28.000Z","msg":"拜登：下？我諗住岀美軍打印度架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1b9d7cb9345be223ed96c0e868d96